Drove to order a few takeaway food items from the NEwest branch. Server forgot to pass me one of my orders and I had to drive back to ask for it. I have to say the curry tasted sour and the quality of the prata and murtabak quality has severely deteriorated. The kosong prata was too oily and dense. The Bee Hoon Goreng was bland and very greasy. The murtabak was too oily compared to the last time I had it there. Maybe the chef was changed but I‚Äôm definitely not going back to try it again.
Best branch ever. Carol, at the cashier, has been very friendly and even able to recommend the dishes and drinks. The cherry on top is that this place is 24 hours!
